WEBVTT

00:00:01.056 --> 00:00:03.182
Adam Grant: I know
you have some pet peeves.

00:00:03.206 --> 00:00:04.571
Everyone does.

00:00:04.595 --> 00:00:07.048
Mine include the guy
in front of me on the airplane

00:00:07.072 --> 00:00:09.816
who reclines his seat
right onto my laptop,

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:13.098
the phrase "everything
happens for a reason,"

00:00:13.122 --> 00:00:14.272
and glitter.

00:00:14.923 --> 00:00:18.359
Whether it arrives on clothes
or holiday cards or presents,

00:00:18.383 --> 00:00:21.240
it always ends up all over me.

00:00:21.752 --> 00:00:23.877
I'm pretty sure that
in all of human history,

00:00:23.901 --> 00:00:26.278
no one has ever benefited from glitter.

